    "title": "IRGC says Dimona,\u00a0Tel Aviv and Eilat\u00a0targeted in new wave of missiles",
    "url": "https://www.middleeasteye.net/live-blog/live-blog-update/irgc-says-dimona-tel-aviv-and-eilat-targeted-new-wave-missiles",
    "content": "<article data-history-node-id=\"436544\" about=\"https://www.middleeasteye.net/live-blog/live-blog-update/irgc-says-dimona-tel-aviv-and-eilat-targeted-new-wave-missiles\" class=\"live-blog-update default clearfix\">\n\n  \n      <h2>\n      <a href=\"https://www.middleeasteye.net/live-blog/live-blog-update/irgc-says-dimona-tel-aviv-and-eilat-targeted-new-wave-missiles\" rel=\"bookmark\">\n<span class=\"field field-title\">IRGC says Dimona,&nbsp;Tel Aviv and Eilat&nbsp;targeted in new wave of missiles</span>\n</a>\n    </h2>\n    \n\n        \n    <div class=\"content\">\n                <div class=\"field field-field-text\"><p>Iran\u2019s Revolutionary Guard said it launched a new wave of strikes targeting Israel and US positions, including sites in Dimona, Tel Aviv and Eilat, according to a statement reported by Press TV.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>\u201cWe negotiate with enemies with impact-driven strikes,\u201d the IRGC said, describing the latest phase as having \u201cset a distinct record in the timeline of the war.\u201d</p>\n\n<p>It said missiles and drones were used in the attacks, including Emad and Qadr systems.</p>\n</div>\n      \n  </div>\n\n</article>",
    "source": "Middle East Eye",
    "imageUrl": "",
    "score": 8,
    "fetched_at": "2026-03-24T02:38:23.929614"
  },
  {
    "title": "Iran military adviser says war continues until compensation, sanctions lifted",
    "url": "https://www.middleeasteye.net/live-blog/live-blog-update/iran-military-adviser-says-war-continues-until-compensation-sanctions",
    "content": "<article data-history-node-id=\"436542\" about=\"https://www.middleeasteye.net/live-blog/live-blog-update/iran-military-adviser-says-war-continues-until-compensation-sanctions\" class=\"live-blog-update default clearfix\">\n\n  \n      <h2>\n      <a href=\"https://www.middleeasteye.net/live-blog/live-blog-update/iran-military-adviser-says-war-continues-until-compensation-sanctions\" rel=\"bookmark\">\n<span class=\"field field-title\">Iran military adviser says war continues until compensation, sanctions lifted</span>\n</a>\n    </h2>\n    \n\n        \n    <div class=\"content\">\n                <div class=\"field field-field-text\"><p>A senior military adviser to Iran\u2019s leader, Mojtaba Khamenei, said the war will continue until Tehran receives full compensation and sanctions are lifted.</p>\n\n<p>Mohsen Rezaei said Iran would keep fighting until \u201call economic sanctions are lifted, and legally binding international guarantees are obtained\u201d to prevent future US interference.</p>\n\n<p>\u201cWe see that our armed forces are carrying out operations and activities with strength,\u201d Rezaei said, adding that leadership remained firmly in control.</p>\n\n<p>He also claimed the United States had been ready to pursue a ceasefire earlier, but that Israel pushed for the war to continue.</p>\n</div>\n      \n  </div>\n\n</article>",
    "source": "Middle East Eye",
    "imageUrl": "",
    "score": 8,
    "fetched_at": "2026-03-24T02:38:23.929758"
  },
